The paper discusses an algorithm for computing the nearest lattice point in A_n*, which is a problem related to computational geometry, information theory, numerical analysis, and discrete mathematics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics).
